description:
Stuck on what to play or what to buy? Join TVGS and I list and discuss ten of the most enjoyable games on the PSP that are unfortunately stuck on Sony’s handheld console. Many lesser known games released for the Playstation portable, so let me know your top 10 overlooked hidden gems and best games stuck on the handheld console down below!
